*******API Testing with REST Assured**********


***Prerequisites***
Before running the tests, ensure you have the following installed:

Software	Version	Link
JDK	8 or higher	Download JDK
Maven	Latest	Download Maven
IDE	IntelliJ IDEA/Eclipse	IntelliJ IDEA / Eclipse


***Setup**
Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/sunitakolkar/wap-twitch-automation.git
cd wap-twitch-automation


***Dependencies***
The project uses the following dependencies:

Dependency	Version	Scope
REST Assured	4.3.3	test
JUnit	4.13.1	test

***Test Results***


| ----Test Case------|------ Description------------------|-----------Expected Result------------------------------|----------Actual Result--------------------------------|--Status-- |       
|--------------------|------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|---------- |
| testGetPoemByTitle | Validate poem title retrieval      | Status code 200,title contains "Love's Rose"           | Status code 200,title contains "Love's Rose"          |Pass       |
| testGetPoemByAuthor| Validate poem author retrieval     | Status code 200,author contains "Percy Bysshe Shelley" | Status code 200,author contains "Percy Bysshe Shelley"|Pass       |
| testGetPoemByLines | Validate poem lines count retrieval| Status code 200,linecount should be 20                 | Status code 200,linecount should be 20                |Pass       |



Validation is used on Response StatusCode and Response Body to check the api request is successful and response data is what we expected
